item.description: Morrell's is an undiscovered gem, if you're looking for a good meal and a comfortable place to enjoy it. The atmosphere in the dining room is perfect for families or small groups. The meals are prepared from scratch - fresh and without much wait time. All of the seafood is local, and the menu is quite extensive.  The menu is varied from fish, to steak and pastas.
item.how_to_find_us: Ask for the Girls Just Wanna Have Fun Table
